author: @therealdr.ripvhs
content: So cool you got to go! I saw it in Seattle and it was incredible. I really wish Nick would do a clip breakdown of her iconic “Truth or Dare” documentary, which has been the basis of every concert doc since, and pretty much the basis of reality tv as we know it.
